Class WebSocketHybi

  • java.lang.Object
    • tigase.server.websocket.WebSocketHybi
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebSocketProtocolIfc

    public class WebSocketHybi
extends Object
implements WebSocketProtocolIfc
    Class implements Hybi (RFC compatible) version of WebSocket protocol specification which is used in connection handshaking as well as in frameing/deframing of data sent over WebSocket connection
    Author:
    andrzej
    See Also:
    WebSocket HyBi specification
